{"tid":1899536,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建制派唔係「成功爭取」,係阻止派$10000 既罪人","createTime":"2020-02-26T16:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T16:30:15.000Z","uid":12510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fad88074acdf77457d279928e5c3abd9f6340f61","tid":1899536,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"引用連登仔區議員「<span style=\"color: gold;\">砂窩雲吞雞</span>」既睇法:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而大家抗拒嘅，我估其實大多數唔係派發一萬元，而係所謂嘅「捆綁式」將「全民派一萬」以及「增加警隊資源」放埋一齊呢一件事。<br />\n<br />\n但有一個好殘忍嘅事實要講定出嚟：「寧願唔要嗰一萬元都唔要警隊加薪」呢件事係一廂情願的&mdash;&mdash;因為立法會入面根本唔夠票。<br />\n<br />\n但唔夠票係一件事，陣間最後「因為要通過乜乜乜而唯有贊成乜乜乜」就係另外一件事喇！<br />\n<br />\n我哋必須要搞清楚：我唔抗拒「全民派一萬」，但我始終如一地反對呢一份會財政預算案&mdash;&mdash;單憑警隊預算呢一個部分，我哋大家都應該堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「全民派一萬」唔一定要預算案，其實當時嗰個「抗疫基金」就應該做，需要做。而假如有關「抗疫基金」當日嘅投票結果唔係咁大比數通過的話，可能今日無咁多人擔心民主派會有「因為要&hellip;&hellip;唯有支持&hellip;&hellip;」嘅論調。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我嘅期望係：民主派喺立法會內嘅人仕可以堅定立場&mdash;&mdash;而只有堅定立場，體現到在野嘅抵抗意志先有意思；假如大家毫無抵抗意志的話，咁過唔過半，又有乜分別呢？<br />\n<br />\n相信關心即將來臨選舉嘅人愈來愈多，討論所謂「過半」嘅事宜都慢慢增加。不過其實有一樣嘢我覺得係錯焦點嘅：「過半」與否從來都唔係重點；重點係想「過半」嚟做乜嘢呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得好好, 應該帶風向, 建制派係「抗疫基金」反對派錢, 反而支持財政預算案度派, 令市民遲左到錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJiWdvd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJiWdvd.jpg&h=ff63624f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leunghomanleo/photos/a.330327841238073/493517394919116/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleunghomanleo%2Fphotos%2Fa.330327841238073%2F493517394919116%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplK%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=e27616de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leunghomanleo/photos/a.330327841238073/493517394919116/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"5c94293039bed77433ff9c26f4525aa330500047","tid":1899536,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxdOO4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxdOO4A.jpg&h=19d1519d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac7efacdc22d29e1fee900161af7dc86ff02d9d2","tid":1899536,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T16:26:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08d512921992dd331f3affd5e30b7cfdb67bed09","tid":1899536,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72c1527e4bfc4a29ea2c8ae87b312dfc7935c72b","tid":1899536,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83aUKEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83aUKEA.jpg&h=daf446d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請問上圖真偽</strong></span>"}]}